data.description: Welcome home. This two-story colonial style with a classic brick facade home offers 2159 of living space. With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bath. One bedroom is on the first floor and the 3 plus your primary bedroom upstairs with not 1 but 2 walk-in closets. The open concept layout combining the kitchen, dining and living room. Laminate flooring throughout the open living spaces for a nice flow.  Enjoy your gas fireplace for most of Michigan's crazy season. Attached 2 car garage is nice and convenient. Home has a sprinkler system. Backyard is fenced and backs up to farmer owned field. All appliances stay except washer and dryer. Buyers need occupancy.
